==English==

===Etymology===
From [[w:Latin|Latin]] ''[[divide et impera]]''

===Phrase===

# Divide and conquer is a combination of political, military and economic strategy of gaining and maintaining power by breaking up larger concentrations of power into chunks that individually have less power than the one implementing the strategy.

